2011-02-24  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@murrayc.com>

	Rename Gio::DBus::DBusError to Gio::DBus::Error.

	* gio/src/dbuserror.hg: Rename the class to Error.
	* examples/dbus/busserver.cc: Adapated.
